{"title":"DEIC","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística/DEIC-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Dispositivos Electrónicos\\NCardíacos Implantables\\N(CIEDs)","guid":"nyrduPG12KZ1wHXGqZI4BQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Dispositivos alimentados por batería →\\Ntratar trastornos cardíacos. Incluyen:","guid":"ud8XNNQNEf_2ruWlv34-Xw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• PPMs: Marcapasos permanentes → control de arritmias.","guid":"DhwqgOkrWWbw4e-sfZSFBQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• AICDs: Desfibriladores automáticos implantables → control de arritmias con cardioversión/desfibrilación.","guid":"iJ5Zy7HUDth4FHdDLBtuhw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• CRTs: Terapia de resincronización cardíaca → mejora de función sistólica.","guid":"BwKwsrMUa9qYln15c1J5gw","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Uso:","guid":"uvL5Enbcj-Wk-cP5jF2QrA","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Monitorización/control de arritmias → PPMs, AICDs, CRTs.","guid":"DtYT9ud0PfdL_-AN1tb6RA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Mejora de la función sistólica → CRTs.","guid":"iho66ciwmi-9hQSXdnWghg","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"YvfuvEZxpyxE7FLt2F2kfw","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Durante implantación o por malfunción del dispositivo.","guid":"VPMADooTToPXZV2utU_QIQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• Malfunciones\\Nde ritmo:","guid":"ZSaUGksOT-5jbd1E18Ow-A","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Oversensing: Sobredetección → falsas lecturas de actividad eléctrica.","guid":"O0q0jskeRalNcigZ5mjQvA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Undersensing: Infradetección → no reconoce actividad eléctrica necesaria.","guid":"L50DBU8xtua95iGaLAE0eQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"• Malfunciones de\\Ncardioversión:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Ausencia de choques adecuados.","guid":"AmwfgqQfao0hkuRzXajOyA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Choques inapropiados.","guid":"artugq-KqkQ9-Jx8-sqWQw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"1","text":"Manejo:","guid":"eWaTcAp7NlRiqp__S16rzg","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Interrogación CIED.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Tratamiento de arritmias subyacentes/resultantes.","guid":"Ski2E3xluMki71NzQpObzQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Tipos de Dispositivos Electrónicos\\NCardíacos Implantables (CIEDs)","guid":"Q84dYh12wu--7EbM0qce4w","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"1. Marcapasos Permanentes (PPMs):","guid":"0lUE9BOnMDPWpHAfurH2DA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Función: Paceo cardíaco → mantener frecuencia cardíaca adecuada en bradiarritmia.","guid":"DZ4BLYa58Syeky1tjdbxQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"2. Desfibriladores Automáticos\\NImplantables (AICDs):","guid":"_Q10HjEfKHLeRLr5Tquwpw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Función: Choques eléctricos → finalizar taquiarritmias ventriculares.","guid":"CRP6dJzpyfZe4ECq7B5gDQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• AICDs transvenosos → también capaces de paceo cardíaco en bradiarritmia.","guid":"nY84_2chyZO5SB7rKNG8Bg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"3. Dispositivos de Terapia de\\NResincronización Cardíaca (CRTs):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Función: Paceo biventricular (VD y VI) → mejora del gasto cardíaco en insuficiencia cardíaca.","guid":"qplv1VdNLhlKOkOi48bziA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• CRT-P: Marcapasos biventricular.","guid":"x6bYZ37jx9vE3ycoCDMV2g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• CRT-D: Marcapasos biventricular + desfibrilador (AICD).","guid":"fa9gqyVSJ_Dk1IPJLNG3VA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"Comparación de\\NPPMs, AICDs y CRTs","guid":"zi3GpyhYncM4VwiTY1FoHw","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Funciones","guid":"U6dYmsjp8q7-GMmzObYHHA","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• PPMs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Paceo antibradicardia.","guid":"yTyvb23oMDyPPRk3wxQ8zg","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"• AICDs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Subcutáneo: desfibrilación (choques de alta energía no sincronizados).","guid":"1sC3PwuVjVtATCAupukJAw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Transvenoso: desfibrilación, cardioversión sincronizada,\\Npaceo antitaquicardia y antibradicardia.","guid":"ZUKKPvHaBV72pdUmAbmgMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"• CRTs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• CRT-P: Paceo biventricular, paceo antibradicardia.","guid":"LQMWmg5Lcp-FRh-LI8rroQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• CRT-D: Paceo biventricular, paceo antibradicardia, desfibrilación.","guid":"SNjsS3AQXLXybTdJxMZ5Uw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"30","text":"Tipos básicos","guid":"GEtnl-xFcqA1RW5Y6Zl6yw","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• PPMs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Cámara única (generalmente VD).","guid":"3Jam7UAxK9VLX8f_tm60Ug","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Cámara dual (VD y AD).","guid":"KgoYTjjAKDMFZQnmCEn6WQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"• Triple cámara (AD, VD, seno coronario → adyacente a VI).","guid":"QwCFXfRcgCdscj7q9HE8sQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"30","text":"Indicaciones\\Ncomunes","guid":"DS9lv_byT_-mRe5-TEvSCA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• PPMs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• SND sintomático.","guid":"c2BcmQLjHfYy8u_2RcD7vQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Bloqueo AV sintomático.","guid":"QOEFeFoIxKxMu1HDW_QtUQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"• Bloqueo AV de alto riesgo.","guid":"UWf13JN4xRZcAx6R2Upm4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"• AICDs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Profilaxis primaria: riesgo ↑ muerte súbita.","guid":"Oad07bbCur2PfowNpl9nIw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Profilaxis secundaria: posterior a flutter o fibrilación ventricular (no asociado a IAM).","guid":"yAjor-0QSqK-rxc6at8oOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"45","text":"• CRTs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Pacientes seleccionados con IC.","guid":"fxyuHAFwN_DBaL-7Ua0Nkg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"Estructura Técnica\\Nde CIEDs","guid":"vc_vxRch0fte_s8AjoqTUQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"1. Generador de pulso:","guid":"AjR7MJxEGmO0uxN_oRMZdA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• Caja metálica delgada → contiene fuente de poder (batería) y computadora programable\\N→ produce impulsos eléctricos.","guid":"vQ-M9eX8zT23lLO75ZNiVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"2. Electrodos\\N(leads):","guid":"n1W19Mn9Of2MYTMMdef0ow","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Función: paceo, detección y desfibrilación.","guid":"UvrSDTPU-_Q9npLUJAlIoQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Extremo proximal: conectado al generador de pulso.","guid":"ep645yWnt7RsJouQ-cGfGw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"• Extremo distal: anclado al miocardio.","guid":"cVqQk1M9VQg6n-8KxdO3Zg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"• PPM cámara única: generalmente VD.","guid":"lRYzgjC715q_I_E2J7HtcA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"• PPM cámara dual: VD y AD.","guid":"QkvcL8x9bXGcuX1uSeEbfA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"58","text":"• AICD: VD con o sin AD.","guid":"-ZPo-f8BsJqglawVdRDYvw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"58","text":"• CRT: AD, VD y seno coronario (VI).","guid":"-opLqWdte9L1jdmxVzsCpQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"Funciones\\NBásicas de\\NCIEDs","guid":"fi7WzQ7xnOw2X3VX5Urexw","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"1. Electrodos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Detectan actividad eléctrica del corazón → transmiten al generador de pulso.","guid":"BN5Emst337msz02e7-xTFg","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"2. Generador de pulso:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Identifica arritmias.","guid":"Tr1qp5PcVpMpk041hDLEPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"3. Electrodos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• Transmiten impulsos eléctricos del generador al miocardio → paceo o cardioversión.","guid":"PZNbkOEnqLlsj61sAgAJrw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Implantación\\Nde CIEDs","guid":"7mrCCjweKjJskM3ya2fwQA","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"1. Inserción de\\Nelectrodos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• En VD y, en algunos casos, en AD.","guid":"59qoeEGsgstA4gXaW8dyYA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• Vía transvenosa (vena cefálica, axilar o subclavia).","guid":"zojtwLOq8JKtXuul-UMW3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"2. Marcapasos\\Nbiventricular:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Electrodo para VI → seno coronario.","guid":"5k-gYE1wP7gn1OGfB2YG6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"3. Generador de pulso:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Implantado en el lado no dominante del paciente\\N→ entre el músculo pectoral y la fascia muscular.","guid":"TTwh-dy-lmeEKOR21jQhzw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Marcapasos\\NPermanentes\\N(PPMs)","guid":"F5HXwZaigEd9sp8WwtXbmw","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• CIED con generador de pulso y ≥1 electrodo de paceo.","guid":"tnLI4VIbKAFHAbrRRjxzvw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Previene bradicardia y asistolia.","guid":"VD_DWM4NoNg53BFDTCuaLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"• Otros CIEDs (AICDs, CRTs) → incluyen funciones de marcapasos.","guid":"2TBaRJWEqZQPg0QDsJvQ4w","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"• Implantación de PPM → precedida por paceo cardíaco temporal en casos agudos.","guid":"e3NSET0F4OXR7W4h3y8YcQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"0","text":"Tipos de\\NPPMs:","guid":"uLTx87IObLBeRzNV5A9vNw","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"1. Marcapasos de cámara única:","guid":"QncVIr-CrjowUMynnYe8kg","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• 1 electrodo → generalmente en VD.","guid":"0c1byPRZn-IJfFpuoZUWPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"2. Marcapasos de cámara dual:","guid":"eYj4scewPoBvnEEOrjv0zg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• 2 electrodos → uno en AD y otro en VD.","guid":"TA2DBGj5uB_GgU2wsJAeoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"3. Otros CIEDs con\\Nfunciones de marcapasos:","guid":"vj5Np-wNKC-Uc9fdMAkC3A","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• PPM + AICD combinado: Ver “AICDs transvenosos”.","guid":"me43imlK1UDSeW5-FwnxFg","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• Marcapasos biventricular: Ver “Terapia de resincronización cardíaca (CRT)”.","guid":"O60FrjGMT2wZgxrppV00gg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":94,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Bioestadística","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística","filename":"DEIC-2024","id":"map_190","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"DEIC-2024"}